      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Because I knew:",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " therefore I gave thee the more and clearer demonstrations of my Divine nature and providence, because I knew thou wast an unbelieving and perverse nation, that would not easily nor willingly be convinced. ",
